      "description": "$34,800 - Ready for your next adventure? This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-loved, offering a smooth and dependable ride that's perfect for your daily commute or weekend getaways! It features a clean interior and has been well-maintained over the years. While you might find some light, expected wear from regular use, it remains a fantastic, high-quality choice for anyone seeking a reliable and stylish car.",
