    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting or a solid foundation for a restoration project. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few stains, though all essential controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance or minor repairs to reach its peak performance.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
